videos.description: On the first possession of the game, Dillon Brooks throws down a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Brooks sets the tone with a ferocious dunk

videos.description: Jordan Bell finds Dillon Brooks for the 3-pointer as Oregon starts the game hot.
videos.headline: Brooks buries the catch-and-shoot three

videos.description: After Oregon fails to box him out, Drew Eubanks throws down a putback dunk.
videos.headline: Eubanks throws down the putback dunk

videos.description: Oregon tried to double team Drew Eubanks in the paint, it didn't work.
videos.headline: Eubanks puts two defenders on the poster

videos.description: It's the Dillon Brooks show early on in Corvallis as he has 11 of Oregon's first 15 points.
videos.headline: Brooks gets the and-1 layup to go

videos.description: Jordan Bell throws down a ferocious jam with no regard for the opposition.
videos.headline: Bell punishes the rim

videos.description: Drew Eubanks throws down another poster dunk on Oregon.
videos.headline: Eubanks destroys the rim with a monster dunk
